            "      <span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">Bacalah wacana yang ada di bawah ini!</span>\n" +
